<item>
            <title>[PIG-4447] Pig Cannot handle nullable values (arrays and records) in avro records</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4447</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s an example of an avro schema containing nullable values in a map&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;{
    &quot;name&quot; : &quot;nullableRecordInMap&quot;,
    &quot;namespace&quot; : &quot;org.apache.pig.test.builtin&quot;,
    &quot;type&quot; : &quot;record&quot;,
    &quot;fields&quot; : [
        {&quot;name&quot; : &quot;key&quot;, &quot;type&quot; : &quot;string&quot;},
        {&quot;name&quot; : &quot;value&quot;, &quot;type&quot; : &quot;int&quot;},
        {
            &quot;name&quot; : &quot;parameters&quot;,
            &quot;type&quot;: [
                &quot;null&quot;,
                {
                    &quot;type&quot;: &quot;map&quot;,
                    &quot;values&quot;: [
                        &quot;null&quot;,
                        {
                            &quot;type&quot;: &quot;record&quot;,
                            &quot;name&quot;: &quot;nullable_record&quot;,
                            &quot;fields&quot;: [
                                {
                                    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;id&quot;,
                                    &quot;type&quot;: [
                                        &quot;null&quot;,
                                        &quot;string&quot;
                                    ]
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s the corresponding Pig resource schema on running it through org.apache.pig.impl.util.avro.AvroStorageSchemaConversionUtilities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;key:chararray,value:int,parameters:[nullable_record:(union:(id:chararray))]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that Pig should unpack the underlying schema from the nullable union and the Pig schema should be&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;key:chararray,value:int,parameters:[nullable_record:(id:chararray)]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s similar behavior if the nullal map value is of type array&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve created a patch with a few testcases written.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
